{"tid":1999614,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"年過30歲的睇書吸引知識方法","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T17:23:40.000Z","uid":228648,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3146a82b91a12e377ce804c54f5f7c6a46215247","tid":1999614,"uid":228648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"30歲後又無睇開書嘅，都會發覺睇書好難(唔計小說)。<br />\n<br />\n我就用自己經驗同大家分享下。(唔計小說)<br />\n<br />\n1) 30歲之後，集中力奇差，集中唔到精神<br />\n<br />\n方法: 睇電子書，pdf用chrome睇，裝個google translate extension，highlight成段，然後right click -&gt; translate，會自動copy成段去google translate。咁做作用唔係真係要translate，係要用佢個發音功能，變有聲書！係就係機械合成語音，但勝在中英都得。用聽比睇更易集中同更易記憶。<br />\n<br />\n2) 30歲之後，身體每況越下，由其是毒L無做開運動，睡眠質素又差，睇一陣書就好攰，個腦好似有層霧罩住咁<br />\n<br />\n方法: 每睇到攰就坐喺度hup一陣，唔好趴喺度hup，要坐喺張櫈，無support咁hup。呢種咁唔穩定嘅睡姿會令你好快醒(15min內)，千祈唔好睇少呢15分鐘，醒返之後就好似電腦reboot咁，集中力+理解能力+記憶力都reboot埋，可以維持幾個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n3) 諗到再講"},{"pid":"97abf0049adf3df1f2cc0f3800735cb418281109","tid":1999614,"uid":21558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"我寫note同寫讀後感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲勤力過讀書<br />\n專注力真係差咗好多"},{"pid":"0f6a7ca306c8c91dbc8e5342d9a663489c1911bc","tid":1999614,"uid":254388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f9e1ed837d90ee3969641afff524da436854381","tid":1999614,"uid":228648,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f6a7ca306c8c91dbc8e5342d9a663489c1911bc","tid":1999614,"uid":254388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"你有追求學問嘅慾望自然會去揾書睇，就算睇唔得耐都會開個頭。去圖書館借書睇，就算睇唔得耐都會借左先。<br />\n<br />\n如果你無試過，證明你無嘅種慾望。何不做返自己更開心？"},{"pid":"c919b731ff51e16442ff8e2a905da64db3f3d88e","tid":1999614,"uid":292644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0f6a7ca306c8c91dbc8e5342d9a663489c1911bc","tid":1999614,"uid":254388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由甜書開始</span>"},{"pid":"7635053647a720a24f82dd2fed886a0ff9a7442e","tid":1999614,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"每日晨跑30分鐘，唔使做尖都會有精神好多<br />\n<br />\n利：尖能"},{"pid":"982f86fc7de8071251ab8447733f872c7cf63a6c","tid":1999614,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"862354fe77e594a85f247f713b638c0938658c5b","tid":1999614,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982f86fc7de8071251ab8447733f872c7cf63a6c","tid":1999614,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"但呢樣冇計<br />\n朝早要返工"},{"pid":"c20e48157f4d42aac49b2acc6628d6b0d4d8ae31","tid":1999614,"uid":117332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"其實睇書會辛苦點解仲要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我由細都睇開書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同打機一樣都係耐咗先攰，都係一樣既興趣啫。<br />\n不如做番鍾意既野仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ab7a7a930d961d7d0e37d76b8d128093da9f7a","tid":1999614,"uid":228648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c20e48157f4d42aac49b2acc6628d6b0d4d8ae31","tid":1999614,"uid":117332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"其實睇書會辛苦點解仲要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我由細都睇開書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同打機一樣都係耐咗先攰，都係一樣既興趣啫。<br />\n不如做番鍾意既野仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"對知識渴求"},{"pid":"33affe1d0b9afb5e894c9203bbc3da790958c51f","tid":1999614,"uid":24339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"學緊第5語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ffacd83b7c54ecfcaba3fa54b035bf3c774a38","tid":1999614,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"竟然係睇書睇到攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體差出去做運動好過啦"},{"pid":"d50d314cd4b4c9767da860e4d3d773a1983b8faa","tid":1999614,"uid":173375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"睇完一個章節/睇到攰就用筆寫低你學咗啲咩<br />\n只有寫得返出嚟嘅嘢先係學到嘅嘢"},{"pid":"0fea785807cfaa683b92b5203b27ffcd60200477","tid":1999614,"uid":303904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"好多知識真係要睇書先得到，唔係上網睇啲7頭識少少扮代表9up兩句就學到<br />\nbtw你講坐係到hup完會精神個point真係同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09badf8d6256154998c981f04454da5c91125181","tid":1999614,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:32:37.000Z","msg":"youtube有人會介紹書，無時間自己睇就聽人講就算"},{"pid":"b874ba3b47d98fa113c6b4ec6d339c847c26826a","tid":1999614,"uid":254388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97498549b6298f598b3a81833752e7bffad6677b","tid":1999614,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cba2259ab19b9f09b7138cbc1fcdac0c90d72609","tid":19996