個重點係你睇完汲收到幾點,袋到幾多落你自己個袋先難"},{"pid":"3f590ef50bcbac35219aafe12ad78d7a25e6fb11","tid":1999614,"uid":126510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"買audiobook啦<br />\n其次就係，聽你口吻，你30歲之前根本唔似有養成睇書學習嘅習慣<br />\n30歲先黎開始？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGood luck"},{"pid":"ed6a61225eacbc960f0bca88ce4cdc0c7851e9ac","tid":1999614,"uid":311458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"覺得辛苦可能係未搵到自己岩既topic 去睇姐. 如果真係覺得辛苦可以搵下有冇其他方法去學.<br />\n<br />\n利申:未過30"},{"pid":"ea4ed9d62959dab85700c40952c8e8fc4b64188a","tid":1999614,"uid":3690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"用電紙書 姐係e ink水墨mon果隻平板睇會舒服d 我咁樣睇notes會集中d 時間長d"}]}